{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01PbxmhMrxgoXVSDUjL1GDGG","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Wiki Index\n2\t\n3\tA catalog of all wiki pages, organized by category.\n4\t\n5\t## Red Hat AI-SDLC\n6\t\n7\t- [Red Hat AI-First Lessons](redhat-ai-first-lessons.md) — Jeremy Eder's presentation on agentic SDLC, issue-to-PR bots, eval infrastructure, AgentReady, and culture shifts\n8\t- [Outcome Tiger Team](outcome-tiger-team.md) — proposal to formalize outcomes as the upstream step feeding the entire pipeline\n9\t- [AI-SDLC Pipeline](ai-sdlc-pipeline.md) — the three-phase pipeline (WHAT → SHOW → HOW)\n10\t- [RFE Creator](rfe-creator.md) — Phase 1: creates and assesses RFEs in Jira\n11\t- [Prototype Creator](prototype-creator.md) — Phase 2: generates clickable prototypes from RFEs\n12\t- [Prototype Creator Demo — May 14](prototype-creator-demo-may14.md) — full walkthrough of automated + human-in-the-loop workflows (Andy, Beau, Dash)\n13\t- [UX Quality Rubric](ux-quality-rubric.md) — 4-dimension scoring system for prototypes\n14\t\n15\t## Machine Learning & AI\n16\t\n17\t- [Vector Similarity Search](vector-similarity-search.md) — ANN algorithms (HNSW, IVF) for finding semantically similar content via embeddings\n18\t- [Vector Databases](vector-databases.md) — specialized stores for embedding-based nearest-neighbor search\n19\t- [Retrieval-Augmented Generation](retrieval-augmented-generation.md) — grounds LLM responses in retrieved documents via vector search\n20\t\n21\t## Evaluation & Quality\n22\t\n23\t- [Evaluator Super Agent](evaluator-super-agent.md) — automated prototype quality assessment (in progress)\n24\t- [Agent Eval Harness](agent-eval-harness.md) — framework for evaluating AI skill quality\n25\t- [Nielsen's Heuristics & The Jagged Edge](nielsens-heuristics-jagged-edge.md) — AI model comparison using usability heuristics\n26\t\n27\t## Tools & Skills\n28\t\n29\t- [Decision Kit](decision-kit.md) — Decision Driven Develo